00:58:12,660 --> 00:58:21,980
It replaces the anxiety of constantly losing the physical pieces of ourselves with the awe of maintaining a dynamic, living geometry.

833
00:58:22,360 --> 00:58:24,420
It's a much more empowering perspective.

834
00:58:24,880 --> 00:58:32,500
As we wrap up this deep dive, I want to leave you, the listener, with a final, provocative thought to carry with you.

